name: I forget my head at home
name_original: I forget my head at home
description:
After you forget you head at home you try assembly it. You have to collect 5 details: 2 spring, bolt, steal and mechanic eyes. After you do thus you assembly head

Controls

SHOP

In shop you can buy items:

Button 1 - Accelerator, Button 2 - Jetpack, Button 3 - NANO chip, Button 4 - NANO skelet

This items add you speed or jump force.
